src/
├── preprocessing.py    ← functions to handle missing values, feature scaling, train/test split
├── train.py            ← loads data, runs `model.fit(...)`, saves a serialized model (pickle or joblib)
├── evaluate.py         ← loads the saved model, computes metrics (accuracy, precision, recall, AUC) 
                        and saves plots (`docs/confusion_matrix.png`, `docs/roc_curve.png`)
└── predict.py          ← example CLI script that loads new CSV rows and outputs predictions
